  botName: Krobus
  description: Although they have 2 hands and have an excellent biology for ArrowHex,
    the Stasius people are not very competitive as their telepathic ability has made
    them quite peaceful throughout their history. Due to this, they are improving
    in the game, but lack a competitive spirit required to be among the best. Krobus
    is their second best player with very good abilities and will present a serious
    challenge.
